Comment: The classical Symmetrical Defense of the Queen's Gambit Declined. Generally white plays 3. cxd5 and black should not reply 3. ... Qxd5. 4.Nf3 cxd4 5.Nc3 Qa5 6.Nxd4 or 5...Qd8 6.Qxd4 Qxd4 7.Nxd4 gives White a big lead in development. The full article at Wikipedia is here: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symmetrical_Defense
